  "description": "Two-chamber refrigerator with a standard width of the case and the lower location of the freezer. One of the most striking features of the model is that the technique is presented on the market in various colours, including unusual, as for a device of this type, blue, orange and green. It has a double-circuit refrigerant circulation system and various chamber cooling systems. The total useful volume of this model is 304 liters, of which 209 liters are in the refrigerator compartment. The upper compartment is divided into 4 shelves made of high-strength glass, and a fairly spacious vegetable container is provided in the lower part of the compartment. The Liebherr CN 4313 refrigerator is equipped with a DuoCooling cooling system that allows you to set independent circuit temperatures and separately control the degree of cooling of the refrigerator and freezer. The latter also boasts the No Frost freezing system, which ensures the storage of products without the formation of ice and frost on the walls of the chamber. Air temperature control is provided by a convenient push-button digital control system with a display. The refrigerator is equipped with a fast freezing function, which allows you to cool up to -24°C up to 9 kg of food per day. The doors of the refrigerator have a special antibacterial seal and integrated handles, they are easily moved to the other side. There is an audible alarm that sounds when the refrigerator is opened too long.",
